snippet.title: CREST Videos
snippet.description:
CREST is a not-for-profit accreditation and certification body that represents and supports the technical information security market. The channel contains videos that span the cyber security industry, with a focus on penetration testing, threat intelligence and incident response. It includes interviews and presentations from the CREST annual conference - CRESTCon (www.crestcon.co.uk), day in the life of videos on security professionals, other interviews and technical presentations. 

Please visit our website for more information on CREST membership and examinations, find an accredited service provider or download our research: www.crest-approved.org
